'''Eileen''' is the girlfriend of [[Phillip Nichols]].

==History==
Eileen came to the hospital with her boyfriend, Phillip, when he had a hernia. Eileen stayed by his bedside, but was asked to leave before they asked him if he had sex with other men.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
She was dating [[Phillip Nichols]], though she was unaware that he was also having sex with other men.
